# Database Conventions

- Schema files: `src/lib/db/schema/` (one table per file, re-exported in index.ts)
- Use drizzle-zod: `createSelectSchema`, `createInsertSchema`, `.partial()` for patches
- Use `toZodV4SchemaTyped()` wrapper from `@/lib/zod-utils`
- Migrations: `bun run db:generate` then `bun run db:migrate`
- Never edit migration files manually after they are applied
- IDs are text (UUID strings), views/likes stored as text counters
